{"product_id":"whitening-facial-kit","title":"Whitening Facial Kit","description":"\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eIntroducing, our brand-new whitening facial kit offers you a complete whitening treatment in only a few steps! This 5-step whitening facial kit deep cleanses, exfoliates, fades dark spots, and moisturizes with a refreshing mist, leaving your skin visibly spot-less, soft, bright, and clear! A facial kit infused with Five easy steps that give tired, dull skin an instant boost of whitening.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to Use\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eTreating yourself to a facial is one of life’s little luxuries, an at-home facial is the next best choice.\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eNighttime is a great time to start. “During the day, skin is in a more protective mode, but at night, skin is more relaxed and starting repair mode, so it can readily accept extra love”\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStep 1: Whitening Face Cleanser\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eA facial cleanser is to remove dead skin cells, oil, dirt, makeup, and other pollutants from the skin.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eStart by massaging the  Whitening Face cleanser on dry skin first. Then, wet your fingertips and massage them through and remove them with a wash damp cloth or sponge.\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eTo rinse recommended to use a microfiber washcloth to provide lifting action and make sure it all comes off.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStep 2:  Whitening Face Scrub (Exfoliate)\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eExfoliating helps remove dead skin cells from the surface of your skin, and it helps make sure the rest of the products you apply are properly absorbed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eTake an appropriate amount of Amor Whitening Face Scrub and gently exfoliate your face and neck in a small circular motion to upwards direction for 5-10 minutes. Then, remove with a wash damp cloth, or sponge.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e“Someone with oilier skin can get away with exfoliating four or five times per week,”\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e“Someone with drier skin should exfoliate much less, about once a week.”\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStep 3: Whitening Skin Polish\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e“Present micro granules which remove surface dead skin cells and encourage new skin cells to appear, which gives an overall rejuvenated appearance to the skin.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eStart by applying Amor Whitening Skin Polish from the face and go towards your neck. Avoid eye area. Then, wet your fingertips and massage it gently for 5 minutes in a circular motion and then, leaves it for 10-15 mins. Then, remove with a wash damp cloth, or sponge.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStep 4:  Whitening Face Mask\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eWhitening Face Mask is one of the most gentle face masks made to remove dead cells whilst toning and lifting skin, refine skin pores, increase hydration, even akin tone, diminish fine lines.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eApply a face mask, take out a quarter-size amount spread evenly across your face and neck. Avoid your eyes. Leaves it on for 15-20 minutes, then remove with a damp cloth or, sponge.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStep 5: Whitening Face Lifting Massage Cream\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eIncorporating a little massage into your facial not only feels great but also helps to increase circulation and lymphatic drainage. This can result in a dewy, de-puffed complexion. It may also reduce dullness and skin irritation.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e“If you want to use fingertips, you can or you can also use any massaging tool”\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eWork from the middle out, and always go upward in motion, If you’re going to work around the eyes, you need to make sure you have enough product around them. You certainly don’t want to tug that area, since the tissue around the eyes is a lot thinner.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e“With the best Amor products and the right steps in the right order, you can give yourself a luxurious spa-quality facial at home.”\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eINGREDIENTS:\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e•    Whitening face cleanser: Steric acid, sodium lorail ethail salfate. E.D.T.A, sodium ethylparaben vitamin E citreal alcohol.\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e•    Massage cream: Water, White soft paraffin, silicon oil, vitamin E, Cetyl alcohol, stearic acid.\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e•    Whitening mask: Water, titanium dioxide, stearic acid, cetyl alcohol, zinc oxide potassium hydroxide.\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e•    Whitening scrub: Water stearic acid, cetyl alcohol. Soft paraffin, Methyl berabin, Scrub particles, titanium dioxide.\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e•    Skin polish:  Water, cetyl alcohol, Glycerin, Propylene glycol sodium methylparaben.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Nutria Fresh","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":46443347345718,"sku":"","price":3600.0,"currency_code":"PKR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0818\/4958\/1878\/files\/PL_00283.jpg?v=1699550188","url":"https:\/\/nutriafresh.com\/products\/whitening-facial-kit"